---
title: Selection Sort  |  O(n²) · Space O(n) stack
---
flowchart TD
    classDef startEnd fill:#22c55e,stroke:#15803d,color:#fff
    classDef decision fill:#f59e0b,stroke:#b45309,color:#fff
    classDef process fill:#3b82f6,stroke:#1d4ed8,color:#fff
    classDef result fill:#8b5cf6,stroke:#6d28d9,color:#fff

    A([selectionSort startIdx]):::startEnd --> B{"startIdx >= length-1?"}:::decision
    B -- Yes --> C([Return · sorted]):::result
    B -- No --> D["Scan arr[startIdx..length-1] to find minimum index"]:::process
    D --> E["Swap minimum into arr[startIdx]"]:::process
    E --> F([selectionSort startIdx+1]):::startEnd
